<concept id="message-content" xml:lang="en-us">
  <title>Adding Content to Your Message</title>
  <shortdesc>
    The fundamental elements of content that are presented to the recipient are the
    subject and the body of the message.  They are set with setSubject() and setBody().
    You can specify alternative bodies by using addPart().
  </shortdesc>
